snippet.title: Faraway 2: Jungle Escape
snippet.description:
In Faraway you're an adventurer exploring the ruins of ancient temples full of challenges and mysterious puzzles. Faraway 2: Jungle Escape is a relaxing adventure escape game full of new puzzles.


Download iOS: https://itunes.apple.com/us/app/faraway-2/id1270205479?ls=1&mt=8

Download Android: https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.mousecity.faraway2
